-- BP Plans to Flare Gases From Carson Oil Refinery in California to July 19
-- Christian Schmollinger
-- 2010-07-16T00:19:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-16/bp-plans-to-flare-gases-from-carson-oil-refinery-in-california-to-july-19.html

          
          
             BP Plc will flare gases in a planned
event at its Carson oil refinery in California from 5:15 p.m.
local time today until July 19, the company said in a filing to
the South Coast Air Quality Management District.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
